Neo Solar reset the conversion price and ratio on
the convertible bonds due 2016  Previous Conversion Price:      29.35
New Conversion Price:           28.33
New Conversion Ratio:           3529.827 Shares per bond
Effective Date:                 Oct. 25, 2013
 